aa(lp264
VWe all sit at various places at various times on this scale,
p265
aVbut what the law of diffusion of innovation tells us
p266
aVis that if you want mass-market success or mass-market acceptance of an idea,
p267
aVyou cannot have it until you achieve this tipping point
p268
aVbetween 15 and 18 percent market penetration,
p269
aVand then the system tips.
